--- 
name   : execute
title  : Executioner
summary: Killer Commandlines
contact: Trans <transfire@gmail.com>
license: Apache 2.0
authors: [Thomas Sawyer]

requires:
- syckle (build)
- qed    (test)

description:
  Executioner is an OCM (Object Command Mapper) CLI framework for Ruby.
  A subclass of the Executioner base class can define a complete
  command line tool using nothing more than Ruby's own method definitions.

resources:
  home: http://rubyworks.github.com/executioner
  code: http://github.com/rubyworks/executioner
